refentry:
elements abstract abstract Element
abstract &abstract.purpose;
&abstract.synopsis.gen; Description
An abstract can occur in most components of DocBook. It is expected to contain some sort of summary of the content with which it is associated (by containment).
Processing expectations
&format.block; &format.csuppress; Often presented in alternate outputs.
&abstract.parents.gen; &abstract.children.gen;
